---
 drivers/scsi/NCR5380.c    | 94 +++++++++++++++++++--------------------
 drivers/scsi/NCR5380.h    | 11 +++++
 drivers/scsi/atari_scsi.c |  4 +-
 drivers/scsi/g_NCR5380.c  |  4 +-
